{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/jquery/target-elements-by-id-using-jquery","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"jquery","demoType":null,"title":"Selektujte elemente po ID-u koristeći jQuery","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Takođe možete ciljati elemente po njihovim ID atributima.</p>\n<p>Prvo odaberi svoj element <code>button</code> koji ima ID <code>target3</code> koristeći selector <code>$(\"#target3\")</code>.</p>\n<p>Zapamtite da, kao i kod izjave CSS, pišete <code>#</code> pre imena ID-ja.</p>\n<p>Zatim koristi jQuery funkciju <code>.addClass()</code> da doda klase <code>animated</code> i <code>fadeOut</code>.</p>\n<p>Evo kako da sakrijete element <code>button</code> sa ID-om <code>target6</code>:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">$(\"#target6\").addClass(\"animated fadeOut\");\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aeda08826","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":6,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18317,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/jquery/target-elements-by-id-using-jquery"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null},{"link":null,"src":"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"},{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/3.2.0/animate.css","src":null}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<script>\r\n  $(document).ready(function() {\r\n    $(\"button\").addClass(\"animated bounce\");\r\n    $(\".well\").addClass(\"animated shake\");\r\n\r\n  });\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<!-- Only change code above this line -->\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n  <h3 class=\"text-primary text-center\">jQuery Playground</h3>\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n      <h4>#left-well</h4>\r\n      <div class=\"well\" id=\"left-well\">\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target1\">#target1</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target2\">#target2</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target3\">#target3</button>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n      <h4>#right-well</h4>\r\n      <div class=\"well\" id=\"right-well\">\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target4\">#target4</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target5\">#target5</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target6\">#target6</button>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Treba da izaberete element za <code>button</code> za <code>id</code> od <code>target3</code> i koristite jQuery funkciju <code>addClass()</code> da mu dodelite klasu <code>animated</code>.</p>","testString":"assert($('#target3').hasClass('animated'));"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da ciljate element sa ID-om <code>target3</code> i koristite jQuery funkciju <code>addClass()</code> da mu dodelite klasu <code>fadeOut</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(\r\n  ($('#target3').hasClass('fadeOut') || $('#target3').hasClass('fadeout')) &&\r\n    code.match(/\\$\\(\\s*.#target3.\\s*\\)/g)\r\n);"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da koristite jQuery samo za dodavanje ovih klasa elementu.</p>","testString":"assert(!code.match(/class.*animated/g));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/#jquery","dashedName":"target-elements-by-id-using-jquery","certification":"front-end-development-libraries","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlo